description: What we offer is a real share of the profit from advertising in the media space without efforts or diving into a new sphere and time-consuming. Every day we review hundreds of sites, analyze their financial performance as well as technical part than we buy those ones that have passed our selection. The main criteria for the purchase is an ability bringing from 50% profit per annum in a year. This is precisely the yield that we will pay you half of the money earned from, the other half we will invest in the further service development.
